        public void shrink(int maximumCapacity)

      • entries

        public org.mini2Dx.gdx.utils.IntMap.Entries<T> entries()
        Returns an iterator for the entries in the map. Remove is supported.

        If Collections.allocateIterators is false, the same iterator instance is returned each time this method is called. Use the Entries constructor for nested or multithreaded iteration.
